{"tid":1604983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬賽曲係勇武前線既軍歌！","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:49:58.000Z","uid":222614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b207a8b755e64ff7cf682fea9e9b51a590576275","tid":1604983,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"《馬賽曲》（法語：La Marseillaise）是法國國歌，又譯名《馬賽進行曲》<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E8%B3%BD%E6%9B%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%259B%25B2&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1WzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=6973cd6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E8%B3%BD%E6%9B%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n前進，祖國兒女，快奮起，<br />\n光榮的一天等著你！<br />\n你看暴君正在對著我們<br />\n舉起染滿鮮血的旗！(兩遍)<br />\n聽見沒有？兇殘的士兵<br />\n嗥叫在我們國土上，<br />\n他們衝到你身邊，<br />\n殺死你的妻子和兒郎。<br />\n<br />\n副歌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武裝起來，同胞，<br />\n把隊伍組織好！<br />\n前進！前進！<br />\n用骯髒的血<br />\n做肥田的糞料！</span></span>"},{"pid":"04341364c63b50e17f5417f1ab74805284f52c92","tid":1604983,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">面對黑警既衝擊時可以壯膽，大家快啲學識佢！</span>"},{"pid":"59081749ee669abfaf66e7553488042bcd13f903","tid":1604983,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"今次真係同到法國黃背心connect !!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efyAxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efyAxS</a>"},{"pid":"288b2f676e0c89b4918d5e2bce1395ea2ddba01b","tid":1604983,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連結法國黃背心！</span>"}]}